**Málaga, Spain. June 15, 2026.**

Malaga Event Gear (MEG), an audiovisual and event equipment rental service active on the Costa del Sol since 1996, has relaunched its website at [malagaeventgear.com](https://malagaeventgear.com) with a refreshed brand and a rebuilt platform.

The new site keeps what has set MEG apart for years: 100% online booking with fixed, standardized prices, so clients can confirm their gear without waiting on a manual quote.

## A Website Built Around Online Booking

In most of the rental industry, securing equipment still means emails, phone calls, and back-and-forth quotes. MEG built its new site around the opposite idea: browse the [rental packages](/packages/), see the price, and book in one sitting.

Every package lists its inclusions and a clear price up front, whether you are planning a [wedding](/packages/wedding/), a [corporate conference](/packages/mice/), or a private celebration.

## Faster Pages, Cleaner Navigation

Performance was the priority. The site was rebuilt to load quickly on phones and laptops, because the company that handles the technical side of an event should not run a slow website.

Pages are organized by occasion and by need, so the path from "I have an event" to "my gear is booked" stays short.

## Nearly Three Decades, More Than a Thousand Events

The brand is new. The track record is not. MEG has worked in audiovisual production since 1996 and has served more than 1,000 clients across Málaga, Marbella, and the wider Costa del Sol, with delivery and on-site setup included rather than counter pickup.

The Malaga Event Gear team summed up the relaunch this way:

> Our clients do not rent equipment to admire it. They rent it to run an event. The new website makes booking the right gear faster, and the hands-on delivery and setup behind it stays exactly the same.

## Explore the New malagaeventgear.com

Clients and event planners can browse the full range of [event rental packages](/packages/) and read more on the [Malaga Event Gear blog](/blog/).

For quotes and availability across the Costa del Sol, Sevilla, and Granada, the team is reachable through the new site.
